Do I agree with the purpose of the elemental forum? Yes. <br>
Do I agree with the implementation or the way it was presented? No.<br>
Was I going to criticise anyone about it without being directly involved? Not if I could help it. <br>
<br>
The elemental planes forums are totally necessary, and anyone who suggests that the way its creation was handled did not create, or reinforce an already existing division of 'have' and 'have nots' on this server, is wrong. Both situations, no matter what anyone would like to suggest, both can, and do exist, at the same time. <br>
